modName: Argent Iron Armor for CBBE V3
summary: a Retexture of NPR´s Argent Iron Armor
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mode.
-----------------------------------
This ist only a retexture of the KURESE´s original mode
at  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12424
-------------------------------------------------------------
I think this is one of the best Armour for Skyrim,
but the original textures are a litle bit..........simple and with low resolution.
I modifiede the original textures with photoshop

I hope you like this mod

Enjoy

___________________________________
UPDATE

Notes
-please download only the new update version
 dont use both versions

-you dont need the original file from KURESE
 this file has evetythink you need
author: Ilias
